#11905
In the swamp~
You come upon a small clearing in the swamp. Sitting on a log, knee deep in the
cold water is the skeletal remains of some humanoid creature. Its head leans
back against the trunk of a tree. Most of the flesh has rotted from the corpse
preventing you from identifying the type of creature. The head is much too big
for it to have been a human. In fact, the skull structure reminds you of a
large frog. A chill passes through your body. You are reminded of that old
adage about someone stepping on your grave.
~
