#11969
The Grok Chief's Chambers~
The walls and floor of the large room are covered with thick skin rugs which
act to deaden the acoustics of the room.  The center of the room is dominated
by a large sturdy chair which is raised on a stepped platform.  A small
cedar table stands next to the great chair. A gem encrusted goblet sits atop
